│                                                                                            │
│ ### Root Cause Analysis                                                                    │
│                                                                                            │
│ The core of the issue lies in the logic within `OptimizeNonTrivialIFuncs`. The code        │
│ iterates through the basic blocks of the resolver:                                         │
