│ `Callees` was never populated, `Callees.empty()` is true, and the assertion fails.         │
│                                                                                            │
│ The fix is to handle the case where no versions can be collected. If `Callees` is empty    │
│ after checking all basic blocks, it means the resolver never returns a function pointer.   │
│ In this scenario, there's nothing to optimize, so we should simply skip to the next ifunc. │
